cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

The paper proposes a machine learning model for multi-view data, which can be applied to various web applications such as recommendation and target advertising. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the main focus of the paper. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) since it deals with web applications. Additionally, the paper discusses parameter estimation and overfitting, which are related to data science (cs.DS) and computational engineering (cs.CE).
